creator: AltairApps
descriptionHtml:
The most comprehensive application to view detailed information about the stations of the Velib bike rental service in Paris.

- Map of the city with the position of stations showing the number of bikes and the free stands for each station. It includes also the BIKE PATH.
- You can click on a station directly on the map to expand its information.
- The map also shows your current position and it updates when you move.
- List of favourite stations categorized by groups (home, work, friends or general).
- List of stations closest to you according to your current position.
- List of all stations.
- Search engine for stations by number, name of station or address in all lists.
- Several languages available (English, Spanish, French, German and Catalan).
descriptionShort: Application to view detailed information about Velib service in Paris.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
4.1.1:
- New design.
- General optimization.
- Bugs fixed.
